 Lecture ------- - 20-Oct-25 01-Dec-25

WWW

 Stephanie Koonar
                        Lecture -----SU 0900-1550 01-Nov-25 02-Nov-25

B253

 Stephanie Koonar
                        Lecture -----SU 0900-1550 15-Nov-25 16-Nov-25

B253

 Stephanie Koonar
                        Lecture -----SU 0900-1550 29-Nov-25 30-Nov-25

B253

 Stephanie Koonar
                        Lecture M------ 1800-2050 01-Dec-25 01-Dec-25

B253

 Stephanie Koonar
                  This section is a fast-paced, intensive, rigorous, "bootcamp-like" mixed mode condensed course that expects students to be present on all scheduled dates on campus and work independently online for a significant portion of the course. It is aimed at learners wishing to create a marketing plan for a company or product in one month. This mixed mode compressed course is scheduled to meet on campus on three weekends and one Monday evening at the end of the term. The meeting times are as follows: Sat+Sun Nov 1+2, 15+16, 29+30 (each day: class 9am-12pm, lunch 12-1 pm, class 1-4 pm) and Mon Dec 1 (6-9 pm). Students must work independently online to complete additional activities between on campus sessions and write a final exam during the regular final examination period. The demands of this section are rigorous and require unwavering focus and commitment. Students interested in taking this section require special approval by the department and should contact the instructor, Stephanie Koonar (skoonar@langara.ca) for details, advice and to register.

For more information, please email/speak to the instructor as soon as possible.
